&lt;DIV&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
&lt;DIV&gt;I don't see why it would be 'revealing a game secret' for a GM just to tell me "yes" or "no" about whether they still drop and the quest is still possible.&amp;nbsp; If they don't drop, that would just be a broken quest then and not a revealed secret, wouldn't it?&amp;nbsp; (is it just me or are these GMs no help at all lately?)&lt;/DIV&gt;&#xD;
