      <description>Try reading &lt;a href=http://www.paullynch.org/cgi-bin/Everquest-blosxom/VSBL/30hmwar.story target=_blank&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;, on the Hollowshade War.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Both sorts of tendons only drops from mobs outside the caves, from the cubs (etc).  They also probably only drop when the Moor isn't in a war status, and each set of mobs are in their home base.  If a tradeskiller has come along and started the war, and been inconsiderate enough to leave it running, you don't stand a chance of getting the drops.</description>
